BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Toronto Tech Stack Exchange
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/toronto-tech-stack-exchange/
UID:event_314022395@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260401T031849Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260404T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260404T160000
SUMMARY:Dupont Morning Code
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Tech Stack Exchange\n[Summary]\nThis meetup is for tho
 se who are interested in code\, web development\, design\, cloud\, or AI. 
 All levels are welcome\, so feel free to bring your laptop and discuss wha
 t you are working on or what you are learning. You can share your projects
  and ideas with other participants freely. There are outlets and WiFi\, dr
 inks are about $5 for tea\, they take card only.\n\n[Price]\nAttendance is
  FREE. But you need to buy something from the venue.\n\n[Policies]\n\\- We
  do not tolerate harassment of our members\n\\- We remind users that that 
 this meetup is intended for networking and hobby development\\\, and any a
 ttempts at using this meetup event as a dating platform will not be not be
  tolerated\n\nFurther information: https://torontostack.exchange/
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/toronto-tech-stack-exchange/events/31
 4022395/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260329T192928Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260329T192928Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
